Paperwork will be refused if  driver does not have on PPE.



Hard hat, reflective vest, safety glasses, closed toe shoes, gloves.





*       Castlewood, VA loading hours are 7:00AM to 4:00PM
*       Driver must be checked in with paperwork by 3:30 to be loaded same day.
*       First Come First Serve
*       Delivery appointment must be completed and returned to me BEFORE the driver will receive paperwork.
*       All loads must be tarped if required.
*       We DO NOT pay detention requests.



Thank you,



Beth Hurd



Office Manager / Castlewood, VA,



Oldcastle APG

Lawn and Garden Northeast-LGNE
647 Circle Drive, Castlewood, VA 24224



C : 276 594-1170

E: beth.hurd@oldcastle.com<mailto:beth.hurd@oldcastle.com>









CAUTION: This email originated from outside of the organization. Do not click links or open attachments unless you recognize the sender and know the content is safe.



