Good morning!



No tarp, flatbed loads (Conestoga and step deck are fine as long as they can handle the weight.) Please email me your driver's ETA if you would like to cover a load.



I appreciate you and hope you have a great day!



For safety, proper PPE is always required: hard hats, high visibility vests, and steel toed boots. Also, standing on trailers is prohibited. Please scale your loads.



Lenessa Niermeier

Dispatcher



Oldcastle APG #  544  (Previously 408)

Hours Monday-Friday 7 AM to 3:30 PM.

4201 Powell Drive

Shawnee, KS 66226

Send all invoices to: ashgrove.ap@oldcastle.com<mailto:ashgrove.ap@oldcastle.com> Please CC me.



Oldcastle # 513 (Previously 248)

Hours Monday-Friday 6 AM to 2:00 PM.

480 S 16th St

West Des Moines, IA 50265

Send all invoices to: northfield.ap@oldcastle.com<mailto:northfield.ap@oldcastle.com> Please CC me.



# 508 Shakopee MN hours: Monday-Thursday 7AM-2PM and Friday 7AM-1PM. (3/20 this site will close at noon.)



Direct Line/Cell: (913) 660-2834

Fax: (877) 827-5032



W oldcastleapg.com<http://oldcastleapg.com/> E-Mail: Lenessa.Niermeier@oldcastle.com<mailto:Lenessa.Niermeier@oldcastle.com>







Proof of Delivery is required for payment on all deliveries. Failure to include all pages, unclear copies, or applicable signatures, could result in payment delays and/or no payment.







CAUTION: This email originated from outside of the organization. Do not click links or open attachments unless you recognize the sender and know the content is safe.



